    "The following year, Cavalcaselle joined in the 1848 revolutions sweeping Europe.": [],
    "For his part in the Italian revolt, he was condemned to death and force to flee.": [],
    "He settled in London in 1850 working for <a href=\"/scharfg\">George Scharf</a>\u00a0as a illustrator of art.": [],
