    "His trips to France and Austria in 1863, the German states in 1863-1865, and elsewhere expanded his knowledge an expertise.": [],
    "Crowe's and Cavalcaselle's <em>New History of Painting in Italy</em> appeared from Murray beginning in 1864 and soon after in a German edition, edited by <a href=\"/springera\">Anton Springer</a>.": [],
    "The groundbreaking work recast much of art history based upon their chronologies of the artist's individual development.": [],
    "Two subsequent volumes, treating the north Italian schools, appeared in 1871.": [],
